Kl6tfh9LSSlBs7SQLkZzsI-dg&oe=6720E103"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "gymclass_trailer_cover_image_v05.png", "id": "794105814977946", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982516_794105818311279_4409523219033140330_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=C7_VNeLOw78Q7kNvgFFqZz2&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDTHW0mAN6DLEXBwBw7HhX2lxHQM_m5iC0GSjEHUaFdsQ&oe=6720B94B"}, "display_name": "GYM CLASS - BASKETBALL VR", "keywords": ["basketball", "nba", "sports", "social", "football"], "long_description": "\ud83c\udfc0\ud83c\udfc8\u26be GYM CLASS is the top VR basketball & sports game. Experience NBA licensed team courts with full-court games, social worlds for pickup games with friends, and football & baseball stadiums. Rated best on Quest, GC delivers top-notch simulation physics, environments, gameplay, avatars, and cosmetics. Tag your opponents in a fast-paced match, or play rec games - GC is where ballers unite.\n\nDownload free to enjoy:\n\ud83c\udfc8\u26be Sandbox: Football baseball, & more activities.\n\ud83c\udf0d Social Worlds: Connect to the best community in epic environments.\n\u2795 Physics Engine: Use real-life shooting, passing, dribbling in realtime, multiplayer games. Get superpowers w/ insane dunks too.\n\ud83e\udd16 Game Modes: Multiplayer 2v2, 3v3, & 4v4 game modes & AI.\n\ud83c\udfa8 Design Your Look: Complete challenges to unlock cosmetics.\n\ud83c\udfc6 Stats & Matchmaking: Track your wins and improve your skills.\n\nNBA Bundle unlocks:\n\ud83d\ude2e NBA team courts: Virtual replicas of all 30 NBA team courts.\n\ud83d\udc55 NBA team branded apparel: Two different sets of team-branded apparel, a team-branded basketball, and team-branded hat. Additional NBA & team-branded basketballs & accessories is available for purchase separately.\n\ud83c\udfc6 NBA Bundle Challenges: Play games to unlock NBA team features.\n\nGC PRO unlocks: \n\ud83c\udfe0 Private Courts: Customize your world, set your rules.\n\ud83d\udc55 Nextgen Avatars: Design your player w/ max control. Hairstyles, facial hair, body shapes, & height.\n\ud83c\udfa8 Cosmetics: Unlock a wide variety of cosmetics from hoodies, glasses, headphones, & gorilla around w/ banana hats.", "short_description": "\ud83c\udfc0\ud83c\udfc8\u26be GYM CLASS is the top VR basketball & sports game. Experience NBA licensed team courts with full-court games, social worlds for pickup games with friends, and football & baseball stadiums. Rated best on Quest, GC delivers top-notch simulation physics, environments, gameplay, avatars, and cosmetics. Tag your opponents in a fast-paced match, or play rec games - GC is where ballers unite."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://gymclassvr.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://gymclassvr.com/tos", "publisher_name": "IRL Studios Inc.", "support_website_url": "https://gymclassvr.com/support", "website_url": "https://gymclassvr.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "1023770785722696"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SIMULATION", "SOCIAL", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "8353346244749200"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75617320_901289084322532_7352245107606873760_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=x716O5jPBqgQ7k